<h1 class="title">Libertarianism follows from common sense morality</h1>
<p>
Libertarianism follows from simple principles
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b>Its wrong to coerce people</b> (outside of very few specific cases with very good reasons)
(eg: lifeboat taking on water)</li>
<li><b>The government is coercive</b>. Laws are ultimately enforced by violence</li>
<li><b>The government doesn't have special permission to coerce</b>  (Lack of political authority)</li>
</ul>
